{"body": ":+1: needs a test and a changelog entry. I do worry about not adding the route at all, if I add a route, and then run `rake routes` or visit `rails/info/routes` and I don't see the route at all, then I would potentially be a bit confused. \r\n\r\nThis might be more obvious for the case where we're explicitly making named routes\r\n\r\n```\r\nget 'one' => 'test#example', as: :example\r\n```\r\n\r\nBut not as many people will realize this makes a named route as well\r\n\r\n```\r\nresources :example\r\n```\r\n\r\nWe should talk a little about adding the route with warning versus just warning.", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/14866862", "created_at": "2013-03-13T20:36:03Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/9704#issuecomment-14866862", "updated_at": "2013-03-13T20:36:03Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 9704, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/schneems/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/schneems/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/schneems/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/schneems", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/schneems/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/schneems", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/schneems/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://1.gravatar.com/avatar/db953d125f5cc49756edb6149f1b813e?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F6ef42a6eab211ddd71ac423a80b42d15.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/schneems/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/schneems/received_events", "gravatar_id": "db953d125f5cc49756edb6149f1b813e", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/schneems/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "schneems", "type": "User", "id": 59744, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/schneems/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "523d10fbbd354364b900468c"}, "id": 14866862, "issue_url": "https://api.github.co